OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fshowery outbreaks of rain. Turning
OL,7,Fbrighter through the afternoon with
OL,8,Fsome sunnier spells developing and
OL,9,Fshowers becoming fewer. Brisk winds,
OL,10,Foccasionally strong on the west coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be a bright evening
OL,13,Fwith a few light showers. The rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will see further light
OL,15,Fshowers between clear spells.
OL,16,FRemaining breezy on northern coasts.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FRather cloudy in the northeast
OL,19,Fwith a few showers. Drier and brighter
OL,20,Fin the southwest with the best of
OL,21,Fsunnier spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
