OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FPatchy
OL,6,Fcloud and scattered showers on Monday,
OL,7,Fbest of the dry and sunnier spells on
OL,8,Fwestern coasts. Dry on Tuesday and
OL,9,FWednesday, rather cloudy on eastern
OL,10,Fcoasts.
